snippet.title: Rest in Jelly - Greenlight Trailer (2016)
snippet.description:
Add ‘Rest in Jelly’ to your wishlist on Steam now! http://store.steampowered.com/app/513660

Welcome to “Rest in Jelly”, a videogame that will test your platforming ability and precision in ways that will drive you crazy. Control Jack the Devil in his adventure to terminate the fearful jelly rebellion. All you will need is just a button… plus an almost non-human accuracy and nerves of steel.

For more information, you can visit our social networks:

Studio website: http://www.littlemiraclesgames.com
Twitter: https://twitter.com/LittleMiraclesG
